{"tid":2123304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海外港人組織需要大家捐款支持","createTime":"2020-07-24T14:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T14:27:47.000Z","uid":29218,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"3cafda004c7ee56eeaa2be3c0adc262fe49f70aa","tid":2123304,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/weareallhongkongers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fweareallhongkongers&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=a295828d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/weareallhongkongers</a></span></p><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kiKwNmNs8HQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkiKwNmNs8HQ&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=3bde9545\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kiKwNmNs8HQ</a><br />\n<br />\n海外港人組織「Hong Kong Democracy Council US（HKDC）」，17日正式宣佈在美國首都華盛頓成立，積極推動游說工作，爭取美國方面訂立支持香港的相關法例。<br />\n <br />\n正在美國出席有關《香港人權與民主法案》的五人代表團，均出席了成立典禮。<br />\n<br />\nHKDC主要以華盛頓為基地連繫港美兩地，首要任務是爭取美國國會支持通過《香港<br />\n人權與民主法案》。<br />\n <br />\n正在美國耶魯大學攻讀碩士的香港眾志羅冠聰、法政匯思前召集人蔡騏、國際著名民<br />\n主研究學者Larry Diamond，人權法專家戴大為（Michael Davis）亦是新組織成員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23605/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-hkdc-hong_kong_democracy_council_us-23607/hong-kong-democracy-council-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23605%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-hkdc-hong_kong_democracy_council_us-23607%2Fhong-kong-democracy-council-us&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=ec1c691f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23605/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-hkdc-hong_kong_democracy_council_us-23607/hong-kong-democracy-council-us</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20190916/V4W6FNTX42GLFO2SRX6BEKWZHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190916%2FV4W6FNTX42GLFO2SRX6BEKWZHM%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=209be756\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190916%2FV4W6FNTX42GLFO2SRX6BEKWZHM%2F&h=28af495e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20190916/V4W6FNTX42GLFO2SRX6BEKWZHM/</a><br />\n<br />\nHKDC理事會及諮詢委員會成員包括美國聖母大學政治學系副教授許田波、「中國人權」執行主任譚競嫦，新民黨主席葉劉淑儀碩士導師、國際著名民主研究學者戴雅門﹙Larry Diamond﹚，經民聯梁美芬的老師、人權法專家戴大為（Michael Davis），以及正在美國耶魯大學攻讀碩士的香港眾志羅冠聰等。"},{"pid":"4c701b5bb658a7cb83b9e8dbeb8d891ac7c634eb","tid":2123304,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T14:03:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/weareallhongkongers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fweareallhongkongers&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=a295828d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/weareallhongkongers</a><br />\n目前僅得$2,673  raised of $408,681 goal<br />\n大約得0.65%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 hong kong watch 籌款只差少少<br />\n目前 93% <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.justgiving.com/campaign/hongkongwatch2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justgiving.com%2Fcampaign%2Fhongkongwatch2020&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=515fd0ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.justgiving.com/campaign/hongkongwatch2020</a>"},{"pid":"ed53412521c2231a6e957f0907fafb8c684f00af","tid":2123304,"uid":132175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T14:09:12.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"6a218b4d58111624c090df4dab